    \"component\": \"shippingservice pods\",\n      \"reason\": \"High client_error_ratio and error_ratio reaching 60% across multiple pods\",\n      \"evidence\": \"shippingservice-0 and shippingservice-1: error_ratio increased from 0.0 to 60.0; shippingservice-2: p99 error_ratio reached 62.69\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice pods\",\n      \"reason\": \"Elevated client_error_ratio and error_ratio affecting service reliability\",\n      \"evidence\": \"productcatalogservice-1: error_ratio increased from 0.0 to 42.86; productcatalogservice-2: p99 error_ratio reached 40.15\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"Extreme rrt_max latency spike indicating potential performance degradation\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max increased from 10,763 to 732,487,046.56 (1.9999x change ratio) on recommendationservice-2\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_cpu_usage p99 dropped to 0, potentially indicating pod restart or crash\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage p99 decreased from 0.06 to 0.0 (2.0x change ratio)\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**Key Findings:**\n1. **Frontend service** is experiencing severe latency issues with response times increasing by nearly 2,000x\n2. **Multiple services** (shippingservice, productcatalogservice, checkoutservice) are showing high error rates\n3. **recommendationservice-2** has an extreme latency spike that could be a contributing factor\n4. **redis-cart-0** shows CPU usage dropping to zero, suggesting potential pod restart\n\nThe frontend service latency issues appear to be the most critical, as they affect the user-facing layer and could be causing cascading failures to downstream services."}
